  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only can report what happened to me, but the teacher, the homeroom teacher, still his name was [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schulze ?] a party member, the emblem right here, not once did he make an anti-Semitic remark.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't treat us six or seven Jewish students any different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I must say the man was, his behavior was impeccable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course the school was such, it was fortunately the principal-- his name [? was Hinzer ?]-- kept things really in order.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Quite sure, of course, I can only guess, that he tried his best to keep the Nazis out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I must say, I have only pleasant memories of school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not once did I hear an anti-Semitic remark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Later on, however, certain students had to be admitted, and they started really quite anti-Semitic, calling names and harassment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And actually my parents went to see the principal, and he made it clear that he simply cannot dismiss, he can't expel him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At that time, I left the public school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Officially I wasn't required to do so, but the principal said I can't, I did what I-- it would be better if I would leave.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did not-- there was no Nazi teachers because the principal more or less could determine what teacher he wanted, but the students he could not do.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
